Title: Holed Up
Description:
Thank the heavenly spirits for you, $c! I don't know how much longer I could've lasted.

There are other Firebough Nook survivors, I'm sure of it. Will you help rescue them and get us to the safety of Shado-Pan Fallback?
ObjectivesText: Rescue Jin Warmkeg, Ya Firebough, Old Lady Fung, and Sya Zhong.
